**Files to create/modify:**
- [StayOwn-Hospitality/services.json](StayOwn-Hospitality/services.json)
- [StayOwn-Hospitality/src/hub-client.ts](StayOwn-Hospitality/src/hub-client.ts)

**Add services:**
```json
