## Verification

After implementation, verify:
- `curl http://localhost:4600/health` shows HOJAI services available
- Event Bus bridge forwards events both directions
- StayOwn, RisnaEstate, Nexha, REZ-Consumer connect to Unified Hub
- HOJAI AI services respond to requests from any company